                <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr "
                    data-isverify="False"
                    data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/2052448/new_review">
                    <span>我要写书评</span>
                </a>
            <h2>
                    明朝那些事儿（叁）的书评 · · · · · ·

                    <span class="pl">( <a href="reviews">全部 195 条</a> )</span>
            </h2>
        </header>
        
            
            <div class="review_filter">
                            <a href="javascript:;;" class="cur" data-sort="">热门</a>
                            <a href="javascript:;;" data-sort="time">最新</a>
                            <a href="javascript:;;" data-sort="follow">好友</a>
                        <a href="/subject/2052448/reviews?version=1" data-sort="version">只看本版本的评论</a>
